@host = http://localhost:5062

### List orders for a customer (read model)
GET {{host}}/customers/cust-1/orders
Accept: application/json

###

### Get one order summary
GET {{host}}/customers/cust-1/orders/order-1
Accept: application/json

###

### Place order (write model — requires Cosmos)
POST {{host}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "t1",
  "orderId": "order-1",
  "customerId": "cust-1"
}

###

### Ops list (partition = tenant|status|yyyy-MM)
GET {{host}}/tenants/t1/ops/orders?status=Placed&yearMonth=2026-04
Accept: application/json

###

### Cancel / ship (after place)
POST {{host}}/tenants/t1/orders/order-1/cancel

###

POST {{host}}/tenants/t1/orders/order-1/ship

###

